1. Create a table comparing Authentication, Authorization, and Accounting (AAA) by listing at least two real-world examples of each function from popular apps like Instagram, Zomato, or Paytm.
=>AAA Function      Description                                       Examples from Apps (Instagram, Zomato, Paytm)"
Authentication        Verifies ""who you are""                    Instagram: Login with username/password or OTP/biometrics.
Authorization        Determines ""what you are allowed to do      Zomato: Verified users can order food; premium users get faster delivery slots.
Accounting           Tracks ""what was done""                         Paytm: Logs every transaction, login time, and IP for fraud detection.

